description: Inspired by Quinceñera parties in the hills of Mexico and beyond & rooted in partying as a form of immigrant resistance. La Cosecha was started by XOLO. Playing all Spanish, all vinyl norteñias, corridos, rancheras, cumbia and banda classics. Xolo's aim is to bring this music to a new generation.
